## Animation Classes

Use consistent animation timing:

```tsx
// Transitions
<div className="transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
  Animated content
</div>

// Hover effects
<button className="hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition-transform duration-200">
  Hover me
</button>

// Loading states
<div className="animate-pulse bg-gray-200 rounded h-4 w-full" />
```

## Accessibility with Tailwind

```tsx
// Focus visible for keyboard users
<button className="focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary">
  Keyboard accessible
</button>

// Screen reader only text
<span className="sr-only">Close menu</span>

// Reduced motion support
<div className="motion-safe:animate-bounce motion-reduce:animate-none">
  Respects prefers-reduced-motion
</div>
```

## Avoiding Common Mistakes

```tsx
// BAD - hardcoded colors
<div className="bg-[#1C8841]">

// GOOD - use design tokens
<div className="bg-primary">

// BAD - inconsistent spacing
<div className="p-3 mt-5 mb-7">

// GOOD - consistent spacing scale
<div className="p-4 mt-4 mb-8">

// BAD - !important overrides
<div className="!text-red-500">

// GOOD - proper specificity handling
<div className="text-red-500"> // or use CSS variables
```
